{
  "id": "adv_bond_ngs_01_04",
  "title": "伊吹渚4",
  "script": [
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "ngs",
      "speakerName": "伊吹渚",
      "speakerNameEn": "Nagisa",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-nagisa.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/bondStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_bond_ngs_01_04/sud_vo_adv_bond_ngs_01_04-ngs001.m4a",
      "text": "お日様がぽかぽかで、気持ちいいし\nお洗濯日和だなぁー",
      "translations": {
        "en": "The sun is so warm and cozy‚ it feels great\nIt's a perfect day for laundry!",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 0.8,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "ngs",
      "speakerName": "伊吹渚",
      "speakerNameEn": "Nagisa",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-nagisa.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/bondStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_bond_ngs_01_04/sud_vo_adv_bond_ngs_01_04-ngs002.m4a",
      "text": "沙季ちゃんが買ってくれた柔軟剤も凄く\nいい匂いだったし、今日のお洗濯は楽しくなりそう！",
      "translations": {
        "en": "The fabric softener Saki-chan bought for me\nsmells so good. Today's laundry is going to be fun!",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 6.8,
      "sfxList": [
        {
          "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBgm/sud_se_adv_run-out-single-01.m4a",
          "delay": 6933.333333299999
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "mei",
      "speakerName": "早坂芽衣",
      "speakerNameEn": "Mei",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-mei.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/bondStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_bond_ngs_01_04/sud_vo_adv_bond_ngs_01_04-mei001.m4a",
      "text": "うわぁーー！　大変ー！　せっかく洗ったのに～！\n洗濯物になんか白いゴミが沢山付いちゃってるよー",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Waaah! Oh no! I just finished washing them too~!\nThere's so much white fuzz stuck all over the laundry~",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 13.7333333333,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "mei",
      "speakerName": "早坂芽衣",
      "speakerNameEn": "Mei",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-mei.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/bondStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_bond_ngs_01_04/sud_vo_adv_bond_ngs_01_04-mei002.m4a",
      "text": "こっちのスカートにも、あっちのハンカチにも……\n渚ちゃん、どうしよう",
      "translations": {
        "en": "On this skirt‚ on that handkerchief…\nNagisa-chan‚ what should I do?",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 24.4999989827,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "ngs",
      "speakerName": "伊吹渚",
      "speakerNameEn": "Nagisa",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-nagisa.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/bondStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_bond_ngs_01_04/sud_vo_adv_bond_ngs_01_04-ngs003.m4a",
      "text": "わぁ……本当だ。もしかして、誰かのポケットに\nティッシュが入ってたのかもね",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Oh wow… you're right. Maybe someone left\na tissue in their pocket.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 32.5666656494,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "mei",
      "speakerName": "早坂芽衣",
      "speakerNameEn": "Mei",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-mei.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/bondStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_bond_ngs_01_04/sud_vo_adv_bond_ngs_01_04-mei003.m4a",
      "text": "これ、パタパタしても落ちないよー",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Even if I shake them‚ it won't come off~",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 39.8666643779,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "ngs",
      "speakerName": "伊吹渚",
      "speakerNameEn": "Nagisa",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-nagisa.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/bondStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_bond_ngs_01_04/sud_vo_adv_bond_ngs_01_04-ngs004.m4a",
      "text": "芽衣ちゃん、安心して\nその汚れ、落ちます",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Don't worry‚ Mei-chan.\nThat mess can be cleaned up.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 43.7666643779,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "mei",
      "speakerName": "早坂芽衣",
      "speakerNameEn": "Mei",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-mei.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/bondStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_bond_ngs_01_04/sud_vo_adv_bond_ngs_01_04-mei004.m4a",
      "text": "えっ！？　本当に！？",
      "translations": {
        "en": "What!? Really!?",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 49.2666643779,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "ngs",
      "speakerName": "伊吹渚",
      "speakerNameEn": "Nagisa",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-nagisa.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/bondStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_bond_ngs_01_04/sud_vo_adv_bond_ngs_01_04-ngs005.m4a",
      "text": "ふっふっふ～。本当です\n伊吹渚のとっておきを持ってくるね",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Hehe~. I'm serious.\nI'll go get Nagisa Ibuki's special secret tool.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 51.6333310445,
      "sfxList": [
        {
          "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBgm/sud_se_adv_walk-out-single-01.m4a",
          "delay": 7600.000000000002
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "ngs",
      "speakerName": "伊吹渚",
      "speakerNameEn": "Nagisa",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-nagisa.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/bondStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_bond_ngs_01_04/sud_vo_adv_bond_ngs_01_04-ngs006.m4a",
      "text": "お待たせ！　はい、この中に手を入れて",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Thanks for waiting! Here‚ put your hand inside this.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 60.0333310445,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "mei",
      "speakerName": "早坂芽衣",
      "speakerNameEn": "Mei",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-mei.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/bondStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_bond_ngs_01_04/sud_vo_adv_bond_ngs_01_04-mei005.m4a",
      "text": "これって……台所で使う水切りネット？　だよね？\n手袋みたいにはめて、どう使うの？",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Is this… a sink strainer net from the kitchen?\nI've put it on like a glove‚ but how do I use it?",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 64.2666643779,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "ngs",
      "speakerName": "伊吹渚",
      "speakerNameEn": "Nagisa",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-nagisa.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/bondStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_bond_ngs_01_04/sud_vo_adv_bond_ngs_01_04-ngs007.m4a",
      "text": "それで、ティッシュまみれの洗濯物を\n優しくなでてみて",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Use that to gently stroke the laundry\ncovered in tissue scraps.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 75.1999977112,
      "sfxList": [
        {
          "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBgm/sud_se_adv_gasa-02.m4a",
          "delay": 5623.333969100003
        },
        {
          "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBgm/sud_se_adv_gasa-02.m4a",
          "delay": 10366.667302400003
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "mei",
      "speakerName": "早坂芽衣",
      "speakerNameEn": "Mei",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-mei.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/bondStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_bond_ngs_01_04/sud_vo_adv_bond_ngs_01_04-mei006.m4a",
      "text": "こ、こうかな……？　わーすごーい！！\nティッシュが、どんどん取れてくー！",
      "translations": {
        "en": "L-like this…? Wow‚ amazing!!\nThe tissue bits are just coming right off!",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 80.0333310445,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "ngs",
      "speakerName": "伊吹渚",
      "speakerNameEn": "Nagisa",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-nagisa.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/bondStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_bond_ngs_01_04/sud_vo_adv_bond_ngs_01_04-ngs008.m4a",
      "text": "ネットの細かい網目に絡まって取れるんだよ\n地道な作業だけど、一緒に頑張ろうね",
      "translations": {
        "en": "They get caught in the fine mesh of the net.\nIt's a tedious job‚ but let's work on it together.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 87.9999977112,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "mei",
      "speakerName": "早坂芽衣",
      "speakerNameEn": "Mei",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-mei.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/bondStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_bond_ngs_01_04/sud_vo_adv_bond_ngs_01_04-mei007.m4a",
      "text": "うん！　渚ちゃん、ありがとう！\n芽衣のお気に入りのスカートも、これで綺麗になるよー",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Yeah! Thanks‚ Nagisa-chan!\nNow Mei's favorite skirt will be clean again~",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 95.0999977112,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "ngs",
      "speakerName": "伊吹渚",
      "speakerNameEn": "Nagisa",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-nagisa.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/bondStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_bond_ngs_01_04/sud_vo_adv_bond_ngs_01_04-ngs009.m4a",
      "text": "ふふ。どういたしまして……あれ？　芽衣ちゃん\nそのスカートのポケットから出てるのって………",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Hehe. You're welcome… Huh? Mei-chan?\nIs that thing sticking out of your skirt pocket…",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 101.9999977112,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "mei",
      "speakerName": "早坂芽衣",
      "speakerNameEn": "Mei",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-mei.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/bondStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_bond_ngs_01_04/sud_vo_adv_bond_ngs_01_04-mei008.m4a",
      "text": "え？　……あ。うわーっ、ごめーん！\nティッシュまみれにした犯人は芽衣だった！！",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Eh? …Ah. Waaah‚ I'm so sorry!\nThe one who caused the tissue mess was Mei!!",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 112.7333310445,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "mei",
      "speakerName": "早坂芽衣",
      "speakerNameEn": "Mei",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-mei.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/bondStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_bond_ngs_01_04/sud_vo_adv_bond_ngs_01_04-mei009.m4a",
      "text": "すずにゃんから「ティッシュとハンカチはレディの\n最低限の身だしなみですわ」って渡されて",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Suzu-nyan told me‚ \"Tissues and a hanky are\na lady's minimum grooming essentials‚\"",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 121.7666643779,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "mei",
      "speakerName": "早坂芽衣",
      "speakerNameEn": "Mei",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-mei.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/bondStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_bond_ngs_01_04/sud_vo_adv_bond_ngs_01_04-mei010.m4a",
      "text": "そのままポケットに入れっぱなしだったー！\nうう……レディの身だしなみどころじゃないよー",
      "translations": {
        "en": "and I just left them in my pocket~!\nUgh… so much for being a lady‚ look at this mess~",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 129.8333310445,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "ngs",
      "speakerName": "伊吹渚",
      "speakerNameEn": "Nagisa",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-nagisa.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/bondStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_bond_ngs_01_04/sud_vo_adv_bond_ngs_01_04-ngs010.m4a",
      "text": "あはは、いいよいいよ。次から気を付けようね",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Ahaha‚ it's okay‚ it's okay. Let's just be careful next time.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 139.7666643779,
      "sfxList": []
    }
  ]
}